(118 So. 921) LOUISVILLE LUMBER CO., etc., v. CENTRAL OF GEORGIA RY. CO. (4 Div. 361.) Supreme Court of Alabama. March 22, 1928. Sollie & Sollie, of Ozark, for appellants. G. L. Comer & Son, of Eufaula, for appellee. SAYRE, GARDNER, and BOULDIN, JJ., concur.

Rehearing Denied Oct. 11, 1928.

ANDERSON, C. J., affirmed.
